  "title": "GARMENTS SPECIALIST",
  "description": "<p>6 Day Work Week Including Weekends & PHs</p><p>Work Location: 18 Neythal Road</p><p>Company Transport Provided from Lakeside MRT</p><p>Join a trusted name in hospitality support services and be part of the team that keeps Singapore’s top hotels looking fresh and spotless!</p><p>If you are detail-oriented, physically active and enjoy working in a dynamic environment, we want to hear from you!</p><p><strong>What You Will Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Inspect and sort incoming loads for stains/damages;</li><li>Perform final OC checks and packing for dispatch;</li><li>Ensure clean loads are counted and accounted for;</li><li>Follow proper procedures for handling different types of fabrics;</li><li>Support general cleanliness and safety in the work area;</li><li>Report any damaged or lost items to the immediate superior.</li></ul><p><strong>What We are Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Physically fit and comfortable with manual handling tasks;</li><li>Good eye for detail and cleanliness;</li><li>Good knowledge of fabric types and handling techniques;</li><li>Able to read, write and communicate in English with our diverse pool of team and clients.</li></ul><p>Ready to make a clean start? Apply today and be part of a team that delivers excellence.</p>",
